{
  "1392340": {
    "name": "Shop Tycoon: Prepare your wallet",
    "steam_appid": 1392340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/cf2121f55800f987914ba401f75d4b3e.avif?t=1769787803\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >信息</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shop Tycoon》是一款商店经营模拟游戏。你将从一家小店起步，逐步把它打造成拥有停车场、员工办公室和庞大车队的巨型商场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/4b848026e8db91d1abd288bbc2ec3526.poster.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/4b848026e8db91d1abd288bbc2ec3526.webm?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/4b848026e8db91d1abd288bbc2ec3526.mp4?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shop Tycoon》既可以当成没有竞争压力的轻松小游戏来玩，也可以当成残酷无情的商店模拟器——“Bandytko”帮派正虎视眈眈，想要抢走你的钱甚至伤害你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/13d49c80a04ea8e95b4f8bf3f8e0ca5d.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造超市、游戏商店、情趣用品店，或者专门经销优质波兰伏特加。修建停车场，让越来越多的顾客来到你的商店，从而获得越来越高的收入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/5867d504b29991f7022a384d451f1789.poster.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/5867d504b29991f7022a384d451f1789.webm?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/5867d504b29991f7022a384d451f1789.mp4?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩充你的车辆车队，提高商店的周转效率。你还可以雇佣经理来管理车队和员工。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/f2934ddf41d8feeba0f0bf82b2c284eb.poster.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/f2934ddf41d8feeba0f0bf82b2c284eb.webm?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/f2934ddf41d8feeba0f0bf82b2c284eb.mp4?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造公交停车场，把更多顾客送到你这家精彩的商店，以进一步提升收入。同时，你还可以提升公交车以及游戏中其他要素的等级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/31bea942f26cb0ba5f96bb6ca92d0c05.poster.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/31bea942f26cb0ba5f96bb6ca92d0c05.webm?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/31bea942f26cb0ba5f96bb6ca92d0c05.mp4?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一开始，你必须事事亲力亲为（就像一人工作室 Airem 一样），但随着时间推移，你可以开始雇佣员工，例如帮你检查商品、保质期等的经理，或者在店内抓小偷的保安。让你的生意实现自动化，为你赚取更多金钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/fe6f00f1e28a74d9b494a3addae1a3c8.poster.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/fe6f00f1e28a74d9b494a3addae1a3c8.webm?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/fe6f00f1e28a74d9b494a3addae1a3c8.mp4?t=1769787803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全世界扩张你的连锁店，在互联网、电视或电台上宣传你的商店。举办打折促销，并与网络 / 电视 / 电台广告相结合。当你遇到麻烦时，可以通过各种方式贷款……或者干脆永久关门！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/3c867d84995334e2008089d4c2415887.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为顾客提供多种便利服务，如移动支付、购物篮、会员卡等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/611f47c52317a3f5fcf28d96167dd341.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理员工，他们可能会生病或去度假；如果有人想要加薪，你可以解雇这个家伙 ([spoiler]xD[/spoiler])……当然，如果他确实值得，你也可以给他加薪。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392340/extras/e7b81e6a1dce26c73f33acfaa0848875.avif?t=1769787803\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >优点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam 集换式卡牌、表情等内容</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 名人客串 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 自由打造属于你的商店</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 排行榜高分系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 种结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持 29 种语言 + 白俄罗斯语</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 自定义商标（商店、车队等）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam 成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam 云存档</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持手柄、鼠标，也可以只用键盘</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 出售伏特加（甚至可以卖给小孩）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 注意卫生防疫站的检查</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拯救你的生意免于破产，打造一个成功、长久的商店品牌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 轻松舒缓的音乐与音效</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >缺点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须每个月支付房租、税金等费用 :-/</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Bandytko”帮派会让你的生活变得更加艰难 :-(</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于描述字数限制，完整版游戏中还有许多功能没有在这里列出。</p>",
